@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_Dashboard
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Dashboard

actor Recruiter as "👔 Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant DashboardService as "Dashboard\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Xem Dashboard ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Dashboard"
FrontEnd -> DashboardService: GET /api/dashboard/recruiter
DashboardService -> Database: Query statistics
Database --> DashboardService: Stats data
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Dashboard data
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị dashboard

== Thống Kê Tin Tuyển Dụng ==

DashboardService -> Database: Count tin_tuyen_dung (active)
Database --> DashboardService: Count
DashboardService -> Database: Count tin_tuyen_dung (closed)
Database --> DashboardService: Count
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Job stats
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị\n(Tin đang đăng: 5, Đã đóng: 2)

== Thống Kê Đơn Ứng Tuyển ==

DashboardService -> Database: Count don_ung_tuyen by status
Database --> DashboardService: Stats
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Application stats
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị\n(Mới: 10, Đang xem: 5, Phỏng vấn: 3)

== Thống Kê Phỏng Vấn ==

DashboardService -> Database: Count lich_phong_van by status
Database --> DashboardService: Stats
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Interview stats
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị\n(Sắp tới: 3, Hoàn tất: 8)

== Danh Sách Đơn Mới ==

FrontEnd -> DashboardService: GET /api/applications?recent=true&size=5
DashboardService -> Database: Query latest applications
Database --> DashboardService: 5 newest
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Recent apps
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Show table:\n(Ứng viên, Vị trí, Ngày nộp)

== Lịch Phỏng Vấn Sắp Tới ==

FrontEnd -> DashboardService: GET /api/interviews?upcoming=true&size=5
DashboardService -> Database: Query next 7 days interviews
Database --> DashboardService: 5 upcoming
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Upcoming interviews
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Show schedule

== Quick Actions ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đăng tin"
FrontEnd --> FrontEnd: Navigate to job posting

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Xem đơn"
FrontEnd --> FrontEnd: Navigate to applications

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Lịch phỏng vấn"
FrontEnd --> FrontEnd: Navigate to interviews

@enduml
